{"tid":1290960,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"各院校學生會係橋頭堡 一定要守住","createTime":"2019-07-06T16:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T01:14:27.000Z","uid":148440,"like":181,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"23b90d7a661fb75e6a54eb5796c2211e0c906b76","tid":1290960,"uid":148440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:29:17.000Z","msg":"學界今次嘅表現大家有目共睹<br />\n但大家又知唔知佢地內部嘅處境其實好危險<br />\n我總括左唔同院校學生會幹事會嘅情況係到<br />\n<br />\n港大: 親共莊上唔到，依家臨委<br />\n中大: 兩支互撼，依家有莊<br />\n科大: 多年無莊，今年唔夠票上唔到，依家臨委<br />\n城大: 無人肯上，依家臨委<br />\n浸大: 上年斷左，依家有莊<br />\n嶺大: 斷斷續續，今年唔夠票，依家臨委<br />\n教大: 今年唔夠票，依家臨委<br />\n理大: 比較少斷莊，依家有莊<br />\n公大: 多年無莊，依家臨委<br />\n樹大: 親共莊上唔到，依家臨委<br />\n恒大: 班老鬼頂左第二年，依家有莊<br />\n<br />\n可以見到，7支斷莊，4支有莊<br />\n部分仲要有比親共勢力入侵<br />\n情況好危險<br />\n<br />\n希望大家推依個post上去<br />\n比黎緊入大學嘅連登仔知<br />\n入學生會都係一種抗爭 我地需要學界力量"},{"pid":"5dc38ad808d1313544aee07a6c1d3d20d0989886","tid":1290960,"uid":148440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d7c3fb9933ff4a866c2ae4df4bd8d07db712c5","tid":1290960,"uid":148440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:31:10.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc9b5e468e603f0ba6878ea833ab6dfd7ec9665","tid":1290960,"uid":134666,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾港大親共莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7662782bcb841844d0f7f336f15f504f900bcbd","tid":1290960,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b7fd7b459fb4161845bba6e24f24c34c5873eb","tid":1290960,"uid":148440,"like":0,"dislike"